0 You can take stuff from the sack or leave some of your items in there. Your items are shown in the top row, the bottom row reflects the items you will find in the sack. To take out or leave an item, select it using the central button, then choose the quantity using left, right, up and down buttons. Then confirm changes in the menu, choosing "Accept".
1 - Number "7" is the number of items.
2 - Number "12" is the number of items selected.
3 - The left bottom corner shows the item's race.
5 - Number "3" shows the item's level.
6 - The items you can put on are marked with a green tick. You can use only those items that belong to friendly races. An item's level must not exceed yours if you want to be able to use it.
7 - The items that you cannot put on are marked with a red cross. However, you can take them away with you, sell or exchange.
